OL,7,FThe Royal British Legion (RBL) has
OL,8,Funveiled a redesigned "planet-
OL,9,Ffriendly" poppy that ditches the
OL,10,Fplastic stem and core after pressure
OL,11,Ffrom anti-waste campaigners.
OL,13,FThe biggest design change to the
OL,14,Fcentury-old Remembrance Day symbol
OL,15,Fsince 1995 will see it made entirely
OL,16,Fout of paper that comes "from a blend
OL,17,Fof renewable fibres" ` with 50 per
OL,18,Fcent recovered from waste used in the
OL,19,Fproduction of coffee cups, and 50 per
OL,20,Fcent from a sustainable wood source.
